My biologic father give me up when i wasn't born , but my mom married another person , the person that consider like my father . He give me her love like i was his daugther . He learn me much about life,  school, and when i grow up i ask myself about our relationship . Because my father influence my decision professional : i wanna be journalist around the world ( if i can ) . When i'm little child , my dad wached every time , every day the news but he forget that me i wanted see a cartoons. When he is in house and no in his job , i knowed ( or know ?) , i will wach news with him . I hated this but i wached more and finally i loved see news in Paris 24 . Was a ritual betwenn my dad and me , i was 9 years and i tell to my dad : I want that you see me introduce a news in twenty years . Today , i runing for make my dream a reality .
